modDescription:
This mod adds a WW2 style Jeep to the 7 Days to Die. A classic all terrain [vehicle](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-vehicles/), perfect for the end of the world! Crafts with the same parts as the 4×4\. Also tweaked the suspension sound that plays on rough terrain so it doesn’t play as often and is more quiet. Bdubyah assume it will apply to all vehicles.

## Changelog

Added new engine/horn sounds.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/bdubyah/Mods---A19/tree/master/Willy%20Jeep)** for A19  
**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/bdubyah/Mods---A18/tree/master/Willy%20Jeep)** for A18
